data.description: A Cozy & Welcoming Place to call Home. Located on Historic Longwood Drive, this Classic Georgian sits on a sizeable 41' x 258' plot of land with stone paver patio and 2 car garage.  It's an unbelievably immense space perfect for outdoor, pandemic socialization. The house itself allows for an abundance of sunlight to stream into all areas of the interior. Most specifically the large, bay window located in the living room is an ideal place for tranquil, sun filled mornings of contemplation, warm fires at night, or to just be. A separate dining room and cheerful kitchen await you and your guests. The powder room rounds out the offerings on the first floor. Moving upstairs, you will find 3 nice sized bedrooms with ample closet space and a full bathroom. Exceptionally tall ceilings and an open concept arrangement complete with family area, exercise corner, laundry and storage are found in the basement. Situated within walking distance to the 107th Street Metra and easy access to I-57.
